# Architecture & Pre-Test Audit

## System Flow Diagram

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["baseline.py (GPT Agent)"] -->|"1. POST /set_task/t1"| B["server/app.py (FastAPI)"]
    A -->|"2. WebSocket"| C["client.py (EnvClient)"]
    C -->|"_step_payload / _parse_result"| B
    B -->|"create_fastapi_app()"| D["server/environment.py"]
    D -->|"reset()"| E["server/data_generator.py"]
    E -->|"sources dict"| D
    E -->|"hidden_truth"| F[("GLOBAL_TRUTH_STORE")]
    D -->|"LAST_ENV_INSTANCE register"| G[("LAST_ENV_INSTANCE")]
    A -->|"3. POST /grader/t1"| B
    B --> G
    B -->|"grader_func(env)"| H["server/graders.py"]
    H -->|"get_task_data() re-seed"| E
    H -->|"pd.merge O(N)"| I["Score 0.0-1.0"]
    J["openenv.yaml"] -->|"GET /tasks"| B
    K["models.py"] -->|"Action/Obs/State types"| A
    K --> C
    K --> D
```

